weather.description: Decent chance of in-game rain as a line of showers moves through, I don't think it will be heavy enough or linger long enough to cause problems.
Rain looks fairly likely here pregame and in-game. I do think the heaviest of the rain will be before the game and early on, but we could see light rain lingering off and on all game long.
On the windy side, sustained winds 15-20mph, impact to deeper throws and kicks.
